                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">policeman.</hi>) On the 10th of Dec. the prisoner was given into my charge by the prosecutor, for striking him over the head with a flat iron—I went to the prisoner in the back yard—he said, "My father struck me first, and I struck him over the head with a fiat iron.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18461214-name-389" type="witnessName">
