                        <interp inst="t18461214-name-389" type="given" value="JOHN GEORGE"></interp>JOHN GEORGE BRIDE</persName>
                  </hi> I am a surgeon. I dressed the prosecutor's head—he had a wound an inch and a half long, and not quite half an inch deep on the left side of the head—it lacerated the scalp—the edge of a flat iron would do it.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> My father got me between his legs, and hit me with a flat iron, and I hit him again.</p>
